properties.body:
You’ve earned a second chance at picking up the Air Jordan 1 'Pine Green' after missing out on launch day. Sizes are limited, so move fast!
At every turn, paying homage to the past while continuing MJ’s legacy is at the heart of Jordan design. Coming off of 2018’s Black Toe-inspired Pine Green Air Jordan 1 drop, this latest AJ1 does exactly that by tapping into OG Bred-inspired color blocking. This year, a fresh Pine Green tumbled leather anoints the heel, heel collar, toe box, and swoosh. Black tumbled leather and laces provide that classic contrast with a white midsole, while red Nike Air branding on the tongue keeps the style rooted in its heritage. Never to be missed, a pair of black Air Jordan wings clipped to the heel complete the new, but true to form look.

productContent.description:
THE ICONIC 1.


Familiar but always fresh, the iconic Air Jordan 1 is remastered for today's sneakerhead culture. This Retro High OG version goes all in with full-grain leather, comfortable cushioning and classic design details.


Air Inside

The Air-Sole unit in the heel provides the same lightweight cushioning that MJ enjoyed back in his playing days.


Leather Luxe

Full-grain leather provides lightweight support and OG basketball sneaker style.


Classic Cupsole

Why mess with greatness? Stable and supportive, the shoe's cupsole has the same profile and thick stitch detailing as the original.


Product Details

  • Rubber tread with deep flex grooves
